{
	"info": {
		"_postman_id": "customers-collection-001",
		"name": "SuperPet - Customers & Addresses",
		"description": "Complete customer management with addresses and personal data (PII protected).\n\n**Features:**\n- Customer CRUD operations\n- Address management with primary selection\n- Personal data (CPF, RG) with PII protection\n- Status management (ACTIVE, INACTIVE, BLOCKED)",
